node.text:
Coconut matcha smoothie 🍵🥥🥰 using my @womensbest blueberry cheesecake protein 🤤 one of my faaave ways to have my protein lately.  Don't forget I have a discount code TAMMY20 for a discount on my whole @womensbest athlete series💪🏼💸
-
1/2 frozen banana
1 spoonful matcha powder
1.5 cup almond milk
1 scoop protein powder
1.5 tbsp shredded coconut
1tsp hemp seeds (I had none left 😪)
(Recipe is from the TammyFit app)
